PN,34702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784033312
OL,3,CFree trains for all Judes in honour of
OL,4,CBellingham's FIFA World Cup heroics
OL,6,FBellingham, who is from the Black
OL,7,FCountry, scored twice during the
OL,8,FQuarter Final match, to secure the
OL,9,Fvictory and set up a mouth-watering
OL,10,Ftie with Argentina.
OL,12,FA place in the World Cup final awaits
OL,13,Fthe winner.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784033312
OL,3,CFree trains for all Judes in honour of
OL,4,CBellingham's FIFA World Cup heroics
OL,6,FTo honour the midfielder's heroics
OL,7,Fagainst the Norwegians and throughout
OL,8,Fthe tournament, the rail operator has
OL,9,Fannounced anyone who can prove they
OL,10,Fshare the first name of Jude
OL,11,FBellingham can travel for free on the
OL,12,Froute from Monday, 13 July until the
OL,13,Ffinal on Sunday, 19 July.
OL,15,FPassengers hoping to take advantage of
OL,16,Fthe offer will need to provide a valid
OL,17,FID.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784033312
OL,3,CFree trains for all Judes in honour of
OL,4,CBellingham's FIFA World Cup heroics
OL,6,FIt is also accepting any variations of
OL,7,Fa name that can be shortened to Jude -
OL,8,Fincluding Judah, Julian, Julie, Julia,
OL,9,FJudith or Judy.
OL,11,FJonny Wiseman, West Midlands Railway
OL,12,Fcustomer experience director, said:
OL,13,F"Along with the rest of the country
OL,14,Fwe're backing England all the way.
OL,16,F"Jude's performances have been
OL,17,Foutstanding and we're delighted to
OL,18,Fcelebrate his hometown of Stourbridge
OL,19,Fwith this limited-time offer.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
