OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784033312
OL,3,CFree trains for all Judes in honour of
OL,4,CBellingham's FIFA World Cup heroics
OL,6,F"We look forward to inviting Judes
OL,7,Ffrom across the region for a free ride
OL,8,Fon the Stourbridge Shuttle as the
OL,9,Ftournament reaches its final stages.
OL,11,F"We're sure all our customers ` Judes
OL,12,Fand non-Judes alike - will join us in
OL,13,Fcheering on the Three Lions in the
OL,14,Fsemi-final on Wednesday and hopefully
OL,15,Fthe final too."
OL,17,FBellingham, from Stourbridge, joined
OL,18,FBirmingham City at under-8s level and
OL,19,Fbecame the club's youngest first-team
OL,20,Fplayer when he made his senior debut
OL,21,Fat the age of 16.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@OO]
