OL,3,CFree trains for all Judes in honour of
OL,4,CBellingham's FIFA World Cup heroics
OL,6,FNow playing for one of the world's
OL,7,Fmost famous club sides Real Madrid,
OL,8,FBellingham has made more than 50
OL,9,Fappearances for England, scoring 12
OL,10,Fgoals.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/6
